videos.headline: UL's Fleming goes 52 yards untouched
videos.description: Dontae Fleming gets the shovel pass and goes the distance for another Ragin' Cajuns' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UL's Fleming goes 52 yards untouched) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lewis keeps it himself and rushes in the 33-yard TD
videos.description: Levi Lewis couldn't find an open receiver in time, breaks a tackle, and takes it up the middle for UL's first touchdown of the game.
